content.text: Page 11 of The Sea Gate Chronicle. Multiple short articles and personals section. Articles include: Prey's (The lotion of the 'addicted hamburger'), Nodick's, White Castle, Coney Island Beach Knishes, Riviera Pizza, Joe's Focciceria Palestinians, John's Hero's, Extra Bar, Gargiulo's, Carolina's, Jap's, Elminger's, Jack's Good Humor, Spumoni Gardens.
